  "narrative": "An email passed perimeter filters because the sender domain was less than 14 days old and had a valid DMARC alignment for a typosquatted root. A user clicked the link 6 minutes after delivery and arrived at a domain that imitates the corporate SSO. The credential POST was captured at the proxy.",
